        {
          "Description": {
            "TableId": "/Game/UI/JournalData/Entries/ST_JournalEntries.ST_JournalEntries",
            "Key": "RotswornNecromancer",
            "SourceString": "Hatred guides these creatures, a vitriolic disgust at a world too cruel to function. They were once mages who had delved into the secrets of necromancy, desperate for power they were too foolish to wield.\r\n\r\nThe power within them has twisted and rotted, infected by Imaru’s vengeful rage. Their souls have been long hollowed out and now they are driven by a need to infect and corrupt, raising the dead in further service of vengeance.",
